beer.beer_description:
We were all a bit salty, blue and sour at times during 2021 - we've used it to create something beautiful and delicious!

This refreshing beer pours with a purple blush, bursts with blueberry notes, and finishes with a salty edge. Best enjoyed over the festive season with mates - if you have to be physically distant, don't be socially distant. Berry Christmas, Baby!
